Package: dkge
Type: Package
Title: Design-Kernel Group Embedding for Cluster-Level fMRI
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Brad Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Brad Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Brad", family = "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Implements Design-Kernel Group Embedding (DKGE) for design-aware
    cluster-level fMRI analysis. Provides streaming and memory-light estimators,
    leave-one-subject-out cross-fitting, kernel-based design alignment, and
    optimal transport to medoid parcellations. Integrates with
    neuroimaging toolkits such as 'neuroim2', 'fmridesign', and 'fmriAR'.
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
